Add To Mirrored Target Platform plugins used in build to generate models and build all-in-one zip :

java -jar <eclipse_location>plugins/org.eclipse.equinox.launcher_*.jar 
-application org.eclipse.equinox.p2.publisher.FeaturesAndBundlesPublisher 
-metadataRepository file:/<target repository golder>
 -artifactRepository file:/<target repository golder>
 -source <bonita-studio>\platform\repository -configs ANY 
 -append 
 -publishArtifacts